#: ../../source/guides/network/non-custodial-node-setup.rst:80
msgid "Prepare the transaction"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/guides/network/non-custodial-node-setup.rst:82
msgid ""
"So far, the node's main account is a regular account. A :ref:`Multisig "
"Account Modification Transaction <multisig-account-modification-"
"transaction>` will be announced that will turn it into a "
":doc:`../../concepts/multisig-account` with a single cosignatory: the "
"**external account**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/guides/network/non-custodial-node-setup.rst:84
msgid ""
"This means that **any operation** on the main account will **require the "
"signature** of the external account."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/guides/network/non-custodial-node-setup.rst:86
msgid ""
"This transaction will be prepared by the node provider using ``symbol-"
"cli`` and sent to the customer for signing."
msgstr ""

