"The ``--max-fee 1000000`` parameter means that **1 XYM** will be paid for"
" the transaction. Feel free to use a different number after reading the "
":doc:`fees documentation <../../concepts/fees>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/guides/network/non-custodial-node-setup.rst:91
msgid ""
"The default transaction deadline in ``symbol-cli`` is **2 hours**. Use "
"the ``--deadline`` parameter if you need more time to get the customer's "
"signature."
